MENU FILE HEADER (Don't delete)
MENU FILE NAME: $popcontrib/x/xved/doit_menus/menus/file_menu
SOME OF THESE COMMANDS WILL REQUIRE A FILE
NAME TO BE TYPED THEN "RETURN"
Select VED file (vedfileselect)             !!      RETURNTHEN menu_fileselect
List VED files                              !!      menu_all_files
Save the current file on disk               !!      ved_w1
Save all files                              !!      ved_w
Start a new file                            !!      ENTER 'ved '
Save this file as                           !!      ENTER 'w '

Read in a file (give name)                  !!      ENTER 'r '
Read a file in "protected" mode             !!      ENTER 'pved '

Clear this file                             !!      ved_clear
Refresh this window                         !!      vedrefresh
Refresh all VED windows                     !!      vedappfiles(%vedrefresh%)

Turn on "autosave"                          !!      ved_autosave
Get help on "autosave"                      !!      'help ved_autosave'

Quit last non-menu file                     !!      RETURNAFTER ved_q
Write all files and leave Poplog            !!      ved_xx
Quit all files and leave Poplog             !!      ved_qq

Get information on VED                      !!      'help ved'
Menu menu            ----->                 !!      'menu menu'
